Predict the relevance of an answer related to the question asked
Created by: jcsantos@ANT.AMAZON.COM

Deadline: July 22, 2021, 5 p.m. PST

Description
The project focuses on answer selection and uses the WikiQA dataset. Each record in the dataset has a question, answer and relevance score. The relevance score is binary, 1/0 indicating whether the answer is relevant to the question. Further details to accomplish this can be found in your final project notebook.

Metrics description
This contest is using the following metric to measure submissions quality: F1

Target column: relevance
